TopicTitle: 1.1.3 x64 crash while in EVA on kerbin [Logs]

Articles.Content:
The only mod I have is something for the UI.

I have Windows 7 64-bit

build id = 01289
2016.06.21 at 20:49:32 CEST
Branch: master

https://www.dropbox.com/s/24q4s6ij4ak5kuz/career.zip?dl=0
My save folder, it happened from Quicksave #1. The suborbit into the other side of kerbin in an attempt to get to the badlands is already set. I disconnected from the rocket and entered the atmo with SAS and landed. I ended up in grass lands instead. I EVAed my pilot and then took out my scientist. Started taking experiment data by manually clicking from EVA and storing it. I think I crashed when I tried to transfer the boarded scientist from the 1 person capsule to the 2 person airliner capsule so that I could get my pilot to go in the 1 person capsule. I was also deleting unneeded quicksaves from windows explorer while playing the game.
